I had this issue too.

+block

–block


And a large part of it comes down to a single word:



When ingested, SCP-474 will affect the consumer until  the next time they enter REM sleep.
附加记录：    

Because it gives the impression that they become human radios until they fall asleep, at which point they have musical dreams and all the while I had a very janky image of how this thing operates.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

As another little note to better control the flow of information so things are a touch less messy:



Although music is frequently referenced, it has not been broadcast audibly.
附加记录：    

I would move this into the preceding paragraph, after this sentence



Audio broadcast from Alexylva University will begin playing through their mouths, consisting of station breaks and notes associated with that campus' radio station.
附加记录：    

Because as-is now, you're revisiting the content of the station notes right in the middle of detailling the affect the dreams have.








